. Furthermore, our simulation results reveal that the proposed two-time\nscale resource allocation design incurs only a small performance loss compared\nto the case when the IRSs are optimized in each mini-slot.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 7 Aug 2022 20:16:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-09"}
