 Type-II CUs. Numerical results are provided to show\nthat the proposed IRS-assisted ISAC design schemes achieve a significant gain\nover the existing benchmark schemes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Aug 2022 08:27:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-09"}
