he $\\Lambda_{c}^{+}\\to\\Lambda\n\\pi^{+}$ branching fraction. This result, which is more precise than previous\nmeasurements, does not agree with theoretical predictions, and suggests that\nnon-factorizable contributions have been under-estimated in current models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Aug 2022 09:29:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 15 Dec 2022 05:00:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-16"}
